      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. i was worried i might need to go back to the surgeon but if it's just a minor thing i'd rather not deal with the clinic wait times. how long should i keep doing the compress and ointment before i decide if it's actually getting worse? also is there anything else i should watch out for that wouldn't be an emergency?",
